http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/chennai/Crime-Branch-sleuths-interrogate-Pachamuthu/article14617421.ece

The officers of the Central Crime Branch (CCB) Police on Wednesday conducted a custodial interrogation of SRM University Chancellor T.R. Pachamuthu who was arrested for allegedly cheating parents of students seeking medical college admissions and the disappearance of his aide ‘Vendhar Movies’ Madhan.